{"tid":1312873,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【XB1/PC】《戰爭機器5》遊戲將禁煙 沒有任何吸煙鏡頭","createTime":"2019-07-13T15:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T01:02:16.000Z","uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"84f36e51a451e318bade63eed0baf56e158dc532","tid":1312873,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:23:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2310631149207393/posts/2378711239066050?s=100001462264101&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2310631149207393%2Fposts%2F2378711239066050%3Fs%3D100001462264101%26sfns%3Dmo&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=ebd7b248\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2310631149207393/posts/2378711239066050?s=100001462264101&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eRu5PaR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeRu5PaR.png&h=49502916&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>【XB1/PC】《戰爭機器5》遊戲將禁煙 沒有任何吸煙鏡頭</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n　　在遊戲和影視作品中，吸煙會讓角色顯得很酷，但眾所周知，吸煙對身體有害。過去的幾年中，隨著反對煙草產品的呼聲越來越高，越來多的人被迫要么戒菸，要么轉向電子煙。而今天，非常意外的是微軟的第一方遊戲《戰爭機器5》也加入了這一禁煙行列。<br />\n<br />\n　　根據Variety報導，在被禁煙組織Truth Initiative接觸後，《戰爭機器5》將刪除遊戲中任何吸煙鏡頭或描述。<br />\n<br />\n　　《戰爭機器5》聲援禁煙，一方面是為了符合電子競技聯盟出於形象方面的要求，另外一方面也是反菸草組織Truth Initiative在主流娛樂中消除美化吸煙努力的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n　　Truth Initiative CEO兼總裁Robin Koval表示：&ldquo;在流行文化中重新出現的美化吸煙形象無處不在之際，我們對The Coalition在本週末的比賽中將吸煙畫面從《戰爭機器5》遊戲中移除以及電子競技聯盟收錄這款無菸遊戲表示非常歡迎。我們希望這個決定能鼓勵其他遊戲開發商和直播比賽效仿這一做法，通過無菸來提升遊戲的體驗。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　《戰爭機器5》將於9月10日發售，登陸PC和Xbox One，將沒有吸煙畫面。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>《戰爭機器5》將於2019年9月10登陸Xbox One和Steam平台，登陸PS4機會不大</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1245830\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1245830</a>"},{"pid":"952bc3c649040109cface62a6bead8014c41f532","tid":1312873,"uid":14812,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gamingbolt.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/death-stranding-image-6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamingbolt.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2Fdeath-stranding-image-6.jpg&h=11750c64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4266884cd7899353dac70326a99ebcbaef750f7b","tid":1312873,"uid":14812,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:18:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/1d5086ac4e6c8119c0c6791561cd014a/tumblr_ps9yi2G6Hy1r0g0c4o3_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F1d5086ac4e6c8119c0c6791561cd014a%2Ftumblr_ps9yi2G6Hy1r0g0c4o3_500.gif&h=e0ca4c85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de5d9a4e2383f2023188ff017db6ba0a6ad02252","tid":1312873,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:21:40.000Z","msg":"打仗都禁煙on99"},{"pid":"e20787695825d49a72e4e581039b9658f396cabb","tid":1312873,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T19:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"315b6a34ba83a14ebb6b0493d66d11f5fa989014","tid":1312873,"uid":50124,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T22:39:57.000Z","msg":"其實主要係個製作人有童年陰影，所以上集就已經冇咩吸煙鏡頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/GearsViking/status/1149882031024721920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FGearsViking%2Fstatus%2F1149882031024721920&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=09135f03\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/GearsViking/status/1149882031024721920</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRod Fergusson<br />\n@GearsViking<br />\nMy dad smoked.  He died of a heart attack at age 38.  I was 4."},{"pid":"3e95865407a3d41d03f0f88758f13aab7a6be072","tid":1312873,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T23:41:45.000Z","msg":"